## Working with the Codebase

### Running Commands
Always run commands from the root directory using Turborepo:
```bash
bun run dev          # All apps
bun run build        # All packages
turbo run dev --filter=web  # Single app
```

### Adding Dependencies
```bash
# Root devDependency
bun add -d <package>

# Workspace dependency
bun add <package> --filter=web
bun add <package> --filter={{scope}}/ui
```

### Package Naming
Internal packages use scope: {{scope}}
- {{scope}}/ui - Shared components
- {{scope}}/config - Shared config

### Code Style
- TypeScript strict mode
- ESLint + Prettier
- 2-space indentation
- Single quotes

### Testing
Tests use Vitest. Run with:
```bash
bun run test
bun run test -- --watch  # Watch mode
```

### Important Paths
- `apps/` - Application code
- `packages/` - Shared packages
- `packages/config/` - ESLint and TypeScript configs
